xyz.fsgik.common.proxy

类 FsProxy.Builder<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • xyz.fsgik.common.proxy.FsProxy.Builder<T>
  • 类型参数:
    T - proxied type
    封闭接口:
    FsProxy<T>

    public static class FsProxy.Builder<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Builder for FsProxy. The instance built by this builder only supports the proxy of methods in Class.getMethods(), and supports using JDK proxy or cglib to proxy.

    Note JDK proxy only supports proxying interfaces.

      • proxyGenerator

        public <T1 extends T> FsProxy.Builder<T1> proxyGenerator(int proxyGenerator)
        Sets proxy generator:
        • JDK_PROXY: using jdk proxy;
        • CGLIB_PROXY: using cglib proxy;
        • SPRING_PROXY: using spring proxy;
        By default, the builder will check the required libs in current runtime to choose a generator in priority: spring > cglib > JDK.

        Note the required libs need to be present in the runtime environment.

        类型参数:
        T1 - proxied type
        参数:
        proxyGenerator - proxy generator
        返回:
        this builder
